OL,3,CStrikes by London Underground drivers
OL,4,Cto go ahead this week
OL,6,FStrikes by London Underground drivers
OL,7,Fwill go ahead this week, threatening
OL,8,Ftravel disruption for commuters and
OL,9,Fvisitors to the capital.
OL,11,FThe Rail, Maritime and Transport union
OL,12,F(RMT) confirmed that its members will
OL,13,Fwalk out from 12pm for 24 hours on
OL,14,FTuesday and Thursday, accusing
OL,15,FTransport for London (TfL) of imposing
OL,16,Fa new, four-day working week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
