CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776687066
OL,3,CStrikes by London Underground drivers
OL,4,Cto go ahead this week
OL,6,FTfL said services will vary across
OL,7,Flines and urged passengers to check
OL,8,Fbefore they travel.
OL,10,FSome bus routes in the capital
OL,11,Foperated by Stagecoach will be
OL,12,Faffected by a separate 24-hour strike
OL,13,Ffrom 5am on Friday.
OL,15,FClaire Mann, TfL's chief operating
OL,16,Fofficer, said: "We have set out
OL,17,Fproposals to the RMT for a four-day
OL,18,Fworking week.
OL,26,@xD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
