CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776687066
OL,3,CStrikes by London Underground drivers
OL,4,Cto go ahead this week
OL,6,F"This allows us to offer train
OL,7,Foperators an additional day off,
OL,8,Fwhilst at the same time bringing
OL,9,FLondon Underground in line with the
OL,10,Fworking patterns of other train
OL,11,Foperating companies, improving
OL,12,Freliability and flexibility at no
OL,13,Fadditional cost.
OL,15,F"The changes would be voluntary, there
OL,16,Fwould be no reduction in contractual
OL,17,Fhours and those who wish to continue a
OL,18,Ffive-day working week pattern would be
OL,19,Fable to do so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@OO]
